  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The other one that we were six months, we had still the privilege to see him after the war, and we took him to Jerusalem, the same way we did with the offspring of the Placzek.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had only one daughter, and till this day, we're supporting her, helping her, and we also took her to Jerusalem and to be inscribed and be planted in the Valley and in the, in the Alley of the, of the Righteous.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both families are recognized as such.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is my privilege, and by the grace of God.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While speaking about the past, I would like to get into the present and the future.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The present, what we try to do is to establish as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I would admire the, the graciousness of people like Spielberg and many others, who would try to perpetuate the memory of the survivors, and especially of the Kedoshim of the martyrs that they got killed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would only say, with, with the help, now, with having the, so to say, the possibility of establishing museums or places of learning about the Holocaust, which is a great, great achievement.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I strongly feel that the, the, especially the Yad Vashem in Jerusalem, which is a remarkable and an outstanding piece of, of-- collection.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's being-- growing and more and more, because it's, it's expanding of so much more and more material.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even having all this dates, and especially the Washington museum, and the New York City plans for museum, and there's many other towns and cities of museums, it's just-- it's good.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm supporting, and I'm all for it, because they should-- people should not have any doubt about it, what had really happened.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
